1. *Max* voli da vozi bicikl. (Max loves to ride a bike.) 
2. Ona nije znala da *Max* ima brata. (She didn't know that Max has a brother.)
3. Ona je najbolja u školi, svi je zovu *Max*. (She is the best in school, everyone calls her Max.)
4. *Max* je uvek bio ljubazan prema drugima. (Max was always kind to others.)
5. Učiteljica mu je rekla da bude najbolji, da bude *Max*. (The teacher told him to be the best, to be Max.)